x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Minogue-Peck@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Minogue-Peck@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kylie-minogue">凯莉·米洛 (Kylie Minogue)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/orville-peck">奥维尔·佩克 (Orville Peck)</a>在舞台上联手，现场首演了一首名为“Midnight Ride”的新曲目。看看下面的粉丝镜头。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kylie-minogue-interview-brit-awards-2024-indie-pop-folk-new-album-3596517">凯莉·米洛 (Kylie Minogue) 告诉我们接下来会发生什么：“独立流行民谣是我快乐的地方之一”</a></strong></li></ul><p>上周日晚（6 月 2 日），这位澳大利亚流行偶像登上西好莱坞 Pride 的舞台，为加利福尼亚州的 Outloud 音乐节画上了圆满的句号。</p><p>除了播放《Can&#39;t Get You Out Of My Head》和《Padam Padam》等热门歌曲外，这位歌手还邀请乡村明星佩克上台合唱。他们的团队首次表演了一首目前尚未发行的歌曲“Midnight Ride”。</p><p>著名 DJ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/diplo">Diplo</a>也加入了他们的行列，这首歌在 Minogue 当晚长达一小时的演出中进行了表演，可以听到这位“Spinning around”艺术家唱着“<em>让我带你去午夜骑行，宝贝你和我</em>， ”在歌曲中。</p><p> Peck 还介绍了这首歌（通过<a href="https://www.stereogum.com/2266259/watch-kylie-minogue-orville-peck-debut-new-song-midnight-ride-at-weho-pride/news/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Stereogum</em></a> ）：“这是一首迪斯科乡村歌曲，因为，你知道，我们必须做一点我和一点凯莉。它已经酝酿了很长时间了，但我们终于准备好把它推出了。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="凯莉·米洛 (Kylie Minogue) 与奥维尔·佩克 (Orville Peck) 在 WeHo 演唱新歌《Midnight Ride》" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/OaQ9fLCV-yI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>第二天，Peck 在 Instagram 上分享了与 Minogue 和 Diplo 的联合帖子，确认这首歌曲将于本周晚些时候正式发布。</p><p> “这个星期五，让我们带您来一场‘午夜骑行’。现在就预存，”他在标题中写道。 《Midnight Ride》将出现在这位乡村明星即将发行的专辑《Stampede》中。该项目已经见证了他与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elton-john">埃尔顿·约翰爵士</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/willie-nelson">威利·纳尔逊</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/allison-russel">艾莉森·拉塞尔</a>等人的合作。</p><p>您可以<a href="https://orvillepeck.lnk.to/MidnightRide" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预先保存单曲</a>并查看上面 WeHo Pride 现场表演的片段。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C7xFzQ4yB4v/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113